    "Among these, five families are Parents of Deaf Children (PODCs), three are Given the challenge of quantitatively analysing the improvement in Auslan proficiency, we focus on measuring the frequency of APP usage by each family.",
    "As shown in Fig. 4, a concurrent upward trend is observed in the usage of Auslan and the application among the surveyed families.",
    "With the rise in Auslan usage, there is a corresponding increase in the frequency of APP usage.",
    "Although this does not explicitly demonstrate an increase in communication and learning efficiency to our app, the positive correlation suggests that our IACH is well-received and valued by these families.",
